              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 5. inch diameter 4. inch long Harshaw",
                "NaI(Tl) crystal mounted on a 5. inch diameter DuMont",
                "type 6364 photomultiplier tube at 90 degr."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A total of seventeen runs was made with targets of",
                "boric oxide and boron of various thicknesses, but the",
                "final result comprises the results of six runs on a",
                "40-keV thick elemental boron target."
              ]
            }
          ],
